column5: Absolutely loving the google earth download....especially the lake depths layers and other info for google earth! AWESOME!  its just that its for Maine!  Does the MNR have something like this?
They do something similar in BC
Here is the Fish On-line site.  MNR Fish On-Line  Not too bad but I love Google Earth too.

Yeah...i seen that site before...contours are a mess.....almost unreadable for Lac Seul, better than nothing I guess. To have it on google earth in the detail and quality of the other site is awesome though.
